SECTION 5 — ROLE-BASED ACCESS CONTROL PROMPT
====================================================

Prompt to use:
--------------
"Define and implement a role-based access control (RBAC)
system for Sparklenz with the following roles:

ADMIN:
- Full access to all modules
- Can create/edit/delete users and roles
- Can view all reports
- Can manage packages and pricing

MANAGER:
- Can manage clients and subscriptions
- Can assign tasks to staff
- Can view payment records
- Can view and generate performance reports
- Cannot manage users or roles

STAFF:
- Can view their assigned tasks only
- Can update task status
- Can attach Google Drive links
- Cannot view payment or financial data
- Cannot manage clients or packages

Generate middleware functions that check the user's role
before allowing access to each API route. Return 403
Forbidden if the role does not have permission."

